# 第三题：[T3](https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/T750566?contestId=320393)
## 题目简述
求`1～N`中质数的个数
## 题目分析
首先先写出质数筛：
```cpp
void f(int n) {
	a[0] = a[1] = 1;
	for (int i = 2; i * i <= n; i ++) {
		if (a[i] == 0) {
			for (int j = i * i; j <= n; j += i) {
				a[j] = 1;
			}
		}
	}
	return;
}
```
然后在用从1~N枚举
如果当前数是个质数，那么ans ++
最后输出
::::success[正确代码]{close}
```cpp
#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;

const int N = 1e8 + 10;
bool a[N];

void f(int n) {
	a[0] = a[1] = 1;
	for (int i = 2; i * i <= n; i ++) {
		if (a[i] == 0) {
			for (int j = i * i; j <= n; j += i) {
				a[j] = 1;
			}
		}
	}
	return;
}

int main() {
	int n;
	cin >> n;
	int ans = 0;
	f(n + 5);
	for (int i = 1; i <= n; i ++) {
		if(a[i] == 0) ans ++;
	}
	cout << ans;

}

```
